name: SYK_Mild detail adjuster（温和的细节调整器）
description:
可能随时下架……

May be removed at any time……

【更新：已推出体积不到10M的小文件版,效果几乎不变】

【Update: A small file version with a volume of less than 10M has been launched, with almost the same effect】

大江户的”add_detail“和其他同类型Lora会明显改变原有画面的姿势、服装、色彩等，权重高了甚至会有种毛刺感，所以我炼了这个Lora，跟”add_detail“等同类型Lora相比，它更加温和，增加细节的同时却几乎不会改变原有姿势、服装和色彩，并且它对绝大多数Lora支持都很好，调整权重(-1或1……）来增加或者减少细节

"add_detail" and other similar Lora significantly alter the original image in terms of posture, clothing, colors, etc. When the weight is high, it may even create a noticeable jagged effect. Therefore, I have created this Lora, which is more gentle compared to "add_detail" and other similar Lora. While it adds details, it hardly changes the original posture, clothing, and colors. Moreover, it works well with most Lora support. You can adjust the weight (-1 or 1...) to increase or decrease the level of detail.
